        </p>
    </div>
    <a href="/Auth/Login" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-darker-shade to-mid-color text-white font-poppins font-semibold text-lg px-8 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 text-center no-underline cursor-pointer">Get started</a>
    </div>

